SELECT MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE it.info ='rating'
  AND k.keyword LIKE '%sequel%'
  AND mi_idx.info > '5.0'
  AND t.production_year > 2005
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND it.id = mi_idx.info_type_id;

       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
    FROM info_type AS it,
        keyword AS k,
        movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
        movie_keyword AS mk,
        title AS t
    WHERE it.info = 'rating'
    AND k.keyword ='sequel'
    AND mi_idx.info > '6.5'
    AND t.title = 'Shrek 2'
  AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2010
    AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
    AND t.id = mk.movie_id
    AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
    AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
    AND it.id = mi_idx.info_type_id;

SELECT MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
    FROM info_type AS it,
        keyword AS k,
        movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
        movie_keyword AS mk,
        title AS t
    WHERE it.info = 'votes'
    AND k.keyword IN ('hero', 'martial-arts', 'hand-to-hand-combat', 'computer-animated-movie')
    AND mi_idx.info > '7.0'
    AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2006 AND 2007 AND (t.title LIKE 'One Piece%' OR t.title LIKE 'Dragon Ball Z%')
    AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
    AND t.id = mk.movie_id
    AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
    AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
    AND it.id = mi_idx.info_type_id;

SELECT MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
    FROM info_type AS it,
        keyword AS k,
        movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
        movie_keyword AS mk,
        title AS t
    WHERE it.info = 'rating'
    AND k.keyword IS NOT NULL AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'murder-in-title', 'blood', 'violence')
    AND mi_idx.info > '9.0'
    AND t.title != '' AND (t.title LIKE 'Champion%' OR t.title LIKE 'Loser%')
    AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
    AND t.id = mk.movie_id
    AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
    AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
    AND it.id = mi_idx.info_type_id;
